{"tid":1819730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致台灣人","createTime":"2020-01-11T05:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T05:45:40.000Z","uid":2174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"31c9eea2e7a46f894ccd6239884efdb84b1ce1f1","tid":1819730,"uid":2174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T05:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qSMqz8A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqSMqz8A.png&h=ebd63b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你們的一票是決定台灣的命運<br />\n蔡英文可能不是最好的總統<br />\n但她是唯一堅決不受到中共任何控制的人，堅決擁抱台灣的自由民主<br />\n作為香港人，我們不想看到台灣變成下一個香港<br />\n所以請你地，將這一票投給她<br />\n<br />\n光復台灣<br />\n光復香港<br />\n<br />\n香港人上"},{"pid":"effa148969c7263415f1368b2050650df6dfd235","tid":1819730,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T05:21:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjQOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=72a760f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"64e162da5ab28630ca9dedf28823da9f2d7699a4","tid":1819730,"uid":2174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"蔡英文"},{"pid":"04dc032c8537da5b9415246505688cc3f7c4a487","tid":1819730,"uid":2174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T05:28:52.000Z","msg":"蔡英文"},{"pid":"57683cbdf1c6a6dc8de6bfb9e919d40e6ebcec3e","tid":1819730,"uid":320902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T05:31:37.000Z","msg":"English Choi"},{"pid":"9404808d069227a300dc135